msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Uma ungaphandle kwe-United States, sincoma i-NOWPayments (imali ephansi, "
"ngqo ku-wallet yakho). Uma use-United States, i-Stripe Crypto nayo "
"iyinketho. Ungavumela izinsizakalo eziningi bese uvumela abavakashela bakho "
"ukuthi bakhethe!"

