"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"I-widget enamandla, mahhala yokunikela nokukhokha evumela abavakashi bakho "
"ukuthi bakusekele ngekredithi noma i-cryptocurrency (Quai). Ayikho imali "
"yanyanga, ayikho izinkokhelo ze-thrid party – kuphela i-wallet yakho kanye "
"nezinsiza ezamahhala."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Ezinye i-browsers zivimba izilayidi zangaphandle ngenxa yokuvikeleka. Le "
"proxy iyalayisha izilayidi ngomsebenzi wakho ukuze ihlule lezi zinqamuleli."

